title: Youth unemployment rate in Jordan in 2019
summary: Overall Youth unemployment rate has increased over the Year.
Youth unemployment rate is slightly increasing from 2013 to 2015.
The steepest increase occurs in between the Year 2014 and 2015.
The highest Youth unemployment rate, of value 30.9 was reached at Year 2015
The lowest Youth unemployment rate, of value 28.43 was reported at Year 2014
min_summary: In general Youth unemployment rate has stayed the same over the Year.
Youth unemployment rate is slightly increasing from 2013 to 2015.
